// sub.su — calculator subtraction service.
//
// Reads operands "a" and "b" and returns a - b on the real axis.
// Componentwise vector subtraction on real-axis numbers is exactly
// real(a) - real(b). Exact through the kernel for operands within the
// float32 exact-integer range.
function vector on_axon(vector input_axon) {
    return axon_item(input_axon, "a") - axon_item(input_axon, "b");
}
